{
  "stem": "1033.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "There was a chestnut tree in front of it, and one of the branches reached over.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I could then be unobserved and listen to all the people, all the grown-ups talking.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I didn't understand it, but it was a fascinating experience.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Sometimes I heard them looking for me, but I didn't say anything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "There was no sound out of me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I finished the four grades in Szucsi.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And then my grandparents-- there were no further school there, as I said, I was the only Jew in the school-- put me in a Jewish orphanage in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- it was-- excuse me-- very uncomfortable.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- part of this was my mother's overriding angst about being Jewish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was reading various reports.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Kafka was still writing in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Again, this comes to me on reflection.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At the time, I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But there was a high degree of angst.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And eventually, she had to be hospitalized, where she stayed until the Germans took her out of the hospital into the ghettos in 1944.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Anyhow, in 1939, I was put into the Jewish orphanage.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that was a terrible shock to me at first.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "To begin with, I didn't know that I had-- I spoke Hungarian with the dialect of the village.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And kids can be very cruel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I used to say [HUNGARIAN].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And of course, they laughed at me because proper Hungarian is [HUNGARIAN].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I was very miserable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And-- but eventually, eventually I-- I came over it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I should say that my grandparents had a Torah in our own house, and we used to have prayer services four times a year from the neighboring villages.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Jews came to form a minyan.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I remember hiding under my grandfather's white prayer shirt.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And everybody looks so fierce.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
